{"tid":1580184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"921 大家點睇","createTime":"2019-09-19T02:55:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T05:10:27.000Z","uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"10f7982f9c0351db4268590bb8ed9563d7f7a481","tid":1580184,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:55:54.000Z","msg":"見到好多人都話唔好去<br />\n唔好同何君堯班狗硬碰<br />\n拆完即晚起返<br />\n<br />\n基本上都同意，佢地仲有黑警backup<br />\n唔應該去硬守<br />\n<br />\n但係另一方面又唔想俾班大陸狗咁易做<br />\n佢地覺得咁輕鬆又有錢收，之後返去又好似好撚威咁同班同鄉宣傳，唔怕佢地越多越多人，係怕佢地個心越來越雄啫<br />\n<br />\n有冇d遠攻/hit and run戰術可以做下？不如大家研究下<br />\n打擊下佢地都好嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f899e1a7b4a013a804722ca8434ea08766e1472c","tid":1580184,"uid":204888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"一齊去屯門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb06070f16259f49c6ed9cb7ab5527531ed9eb1c","tid":1580184,"uid":104855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:58:25.000Z","msg":"敵進我退呀<br />\n<br />\n緊守不出都係戰略來㗎<br />\n唔一定下下迎擊先係打仗嘅<br />\n孫子話嘅：全軍為上，破軍次之。<br />\n<br />\n如果要做，就係事先喺文宣牆上面做手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b38fbe799bdb28eb472b60e052659dcd4280e493","tid":1580184,"uid":264183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f899e1a7b4a013a804722ca8434ea08766e1472c","tid":1580184,"uid":204888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:57:08.000Z","msg":"一齊去屯門啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:00:40.000Z","msg":"你分左手先喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e421c5b0ab5faf112dbfee844ddf12440095533","tid":1580184,"uid":264183,"l